bring it back to us.

39
00:01:47.941 --> 00:01:48.566
and that's it.
that's the whole thing.

40
00:01:48.817 --> 00:01:50.360
Well. unless of course you--

41
00:01:50.402 --> 00:01:51.778
No. but that really
is the whole thing.

42
00:01:51.820 --> 00:01:53.071
-That's it.
-Don't worry. Mishka.

43
00:01:53.113 --> 00:01:54.572
