67
00:02:45.457 --> 00:02:46.958
And frankly.
I could use a shower.

68
00:02:49.878 --> 00:02:51.004
-Coffee candy?
-Yes!

69
00:02:51.046 --> 00:02:52.797
-Twila: Yeah!
-Bea: Thanks. Baba.

70
00:02:52.839 --> 00:02:54.007
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

71
00:02:55.508 --> 00:02:57.969
