124
00:05:36.086 --> 00:05:37.629
His fault.
He always picked a bad year.

125
00:05:37.671 --> 00:05:39.381
[chuckles] He hated it!

126
00:05:39.422 --> 00:05:40.924
-[Manya sighs]
-"How could any year

127
00:05:41.091 --> 00:05:42.467
