about tonight.

138
00:06:05.615 --> 00:06:10.245
You are lucky enough
to accompany me to the ballet.

139
00:06:10.286 --> 00:06:11.871
Lili and I were supposed
to take my counterpart

140
00:06:11.913 --> 00:06:13.915
