162
00:07:07.302 --> 00:07:09.512
-You--
-She's cheating on you.

163
00:07:12.932 --> 00:07:14.559
-Wait. what?

164
00:07:14.601 --> 00:07:17.312
I mean. you didn't--
see the signs?

165
00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:20.982
Maybe she's been distant lately.

166
00:07:21.024 --> 00:07:23.276
