189
00:08:20.041 --> 00:08:23.044
-They're-- it's subtle.
-The color of shit.

190
00:08:23.086 --> 00:08:24.671
-Well. yeah. you know. Vera's
options were kinda limited.

191
00:08:24.879 --> 00:08:27.215
