to shop at Casual Corner.

192
00:08:27.257 --> 00:08:29.175
-No wonder she killed herself.

193
00:08:29.217 --> 00:08:31.261
-She didn't kill herself.
It was an accident.

194
00:08:32.762 --> 00:08:34.848
